text: Serge Cornut (born 6 May 1948) is a French equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haute-Savoie
